msgstr "✅ C# code has been generated to {output}"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:34
msgid "在数据库执行Schema升级脚本,如果没有则创建，如果无变更则跳过。同时还会进行临时表的清空。应该在CI/CD流程中，每次启动服务器前执行一次。"
msgstr ""
"Executes schema upgrade scripts in the database, creating them if they "
"don't exist and skipping if there are no changes. Also clears temporary "
"tables. Should be executed once before each server start in the CI/CD "
"pipeline."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:41 hetu/cli/start.py:100
msgid "后端数据库地址"
msgstr "Backend database address"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:51 hetu/cli/start.py:89
msgid "启动app.py中哪个namespace下的System"
msgstr "Which System under which namespace in app.py to start"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:54 hetu/cli/start.py:92
msgid "实例名称，每个实例是一个副本"
msgstr "Instance name, each instance is a replica"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:58
msgid "通过yml配置文件读取后端数据库地址"
msgstr "Reads the backend database address from the YAML configuration file."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:64
msgid "自动确认数据备份提示"
msgstr "Automatically confirms the data backup prompt."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:70
msgid "强制执行升级迁移，丢弃无法迁移的数据。请勿在生产环境使用此选项！"
msgstr ""
"Forces the upgrade migration, discarding data that cannot be migrated. Do"
" not use this option in production!"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:104
msgid "⚠️  升级数据库表结构可能会导致数据丢失，请确保已备份数据。确认继续请输 y ，取消请输其他键然后回车："
msgstr ""
"⚠️  Upgrading the database schema may cause data loss. Please ensure you "
"have backed up your data. Enter 'y' to confirm and continue, or any other"
" key and press Enter to cancel:"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:109 hetu/cli/migrate.py:136
msgid "❌  升级迁移已取消。"
msgstr "❌  Upgrade migration has been canceled."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:126
msgid "❗ Component有数据删除或类型变更，请修改自动生成的迁移脚本，手动处理这些属性。或使用--drop-data参数直接丢弃这些属性。"
msgstr ""
"❗ Component has data deletion or type changes. Please modify the auto-"
"generated migration script to handle these attributes manually. Or use "
"the --drop-data parameter to discard these attributes directly."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:133
msgid "⚠️  确认强制迁移请输 y ，取消请输其他键然后回车："
msgstr ""
"⚠️  Enter 'y' to confirm forced migration, or any other key and press "
"Enter to cancel:"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:139
#, python-brace-format
msgid "⚠️  正在强制迁移 {instance_name} 服所有表结构，可能会丢失数据..."
msgstr ""
"⚠️  Forcing migration of all table structures for the {instance_name} "
"instance, data may be lost..."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:147
#, python-brace-format
msgid "🧹 正在清除 {instance_name} 服易失数据..."
msgstr "🧹 Clearing volatile data for the {instance_name} instance..."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:150
#, python-brace-format
msgid "✅  {instance_name} 服升级迁移完成！"
msgstr "✅  Upgrade migration for the {instance_name} instance is complete!"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:151
msgid "🎉  恭喜！所有数据库表结构均已升级完成！"
msgstr ""
"🎉  Congratulations! All database table structures have been successfully "
"upgraded!"

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:173
msgid "namespace参数不能为空，建议用--config参数"
msgstr ""
"The namespace parameter cannot be empty. It is recommended to use the "
"--config parameter."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:174
msgid "instance参数不能为空，建议用--config参数"
msgstr ""
"The instance parameter cannot be empty. It is recommended to use the "
"--config parameter."

#: hetu/cli/migrate.py:175
msgid "app_file参数不能为空，建议用--config参数"
msgstr ""
"The app_file parameter cannot be empty. It is recommended to use the "
"--config parameter."

#: hetu/cli/start.py:52
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"不支持的数据库URL scheme: '{scheme}'。目前支持 "
"redis/rediss/valkey/valkeys/postgres/postgresql/sqlite/mysql/mariadb"
msgstr ""
"Unsupported database URL scheme: '{scheme}'. Currently supported: "
"redis/rediss/valkey/valkeys/postgres/postgresql/sqlite/mysql/mariadb"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:77
msgid "启动河图服务"
msgstr "Start Hetu service"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:79
msgid "通过命令行启动参数"
msgstr "Via command line startup parameters"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:95
msgid "监听的Websocket端口"
msgstr "Websocket port to listen on"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:104
msgid "工作进程数，可设为 CPU * 1.2"
msgstr "Number of worker processes, can be set to CPU * 1.2"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:112
msgid "开启debug模式，这会启动代码热更新，并显示更多的log信息。如果设置为2，则对框架内核也启用debug模式，会开启Python协程的Debug模式，速度慢90％。"
msgstr ""
"Enable debug mode. This will start code hot reloading and show more log "
"information. If set to 2, debug mode is also enabled for the framework "
"core, which activates Python coroutine Debug mode, slowing down by 90%."

#: hetu/cli/start.py:122
msgid "证书目录，如果不设置则使用不安全的连接。不建议这里设置，请外加一层反向https代理。填入auto会生成自签https证书。"
msgstr ""
"Certificate directory. If not set, an insecure connection is used. It is "
"not recommended to set this here; please add an external reverse HTTPS "
"proxy layer. Enter 'auto' to generate a self-signed HTTPS certificate."

#: hetu/cli/start.py:130
msgid "默认crypto层的auth_key，用于握手签名校验。留空则不启用。"
msgstr ""
"Default auth_key for the crypto layer, used for handshake signature "
"verification. Leave empty to disable."

#: hetu/cli/start.py:137
msgid "配置文件模板见CONFIG_TEMPLATE.yml"
msgstr "Configuration file template: CONFIG_TEMPLATE.yml"

#: hetu/cli/start.py:155
